{"tid":2224373,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"落大雨跣親柒左點算","createTime":"2020-09-30T12:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T13:56:20.000Z","uid":281826,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"dae78a30b577e62828d396b760e61634b53ab2c2","tid":2224373,"uid":281826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:27:55.000Z","msg":"啱啱落條半露天樓梯 出面落到狗屎咁 我見內側排曬隊貪快行外側 點知仆街了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n踩到個濕撚曬嘅位 對鞋又膠 成個屎忽dun落地下仲要跣左兩三級先停 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身個人放空緊 啊左聲 啲人即刻O撚曬嘴望住我 我只係一個毒撚 好想搵 loan捐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆完點做好"},{"pid":"00e54ecc6bcc3a2667ac69c30c615639639bf546","tid":2224373,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"Nobody cares"},{"pid":"7dc7cb116b73f6ea53d819a50e17b00bb5aa05a4","tid":2224373,"uid":367090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be9d25784d674ee54b026276cb2cd1ba9b7e7ec","tid":2224373,"uid":366655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"你應該大聲嗌<br />\n邊個搞我後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843cb7be2a3925fc1db1f86fd7fd98cce07816d4","tid":2224373,"uid":138834,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"將所有目擊者滅口，目擊者有可能將件事傳左出去<br />\n所以目擊者嘅親朋戚友都要滅口<br />\n因為有可能放左上網，所以所有網絡使用者都要滅口<br />\n你殺到咁上下應該出名到冇網上嘅非洲土著都識你了<br />\n<br />\n順手滅埋<br />\n<br />\n之後應該冇人知你仆街了"},{"pid":"094e57a8e6cc79ae96361c4e86507a5f6dff9846","tid":2224373,"uid":281826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc7cb116b73f6ea53d819a50e17b00bb5aa05a4","tid":2224373,"uid":367090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" c